headline.main: Mason Leads No. 1 Kansas Past Oklahoma State, 90-85
headline.print_headline: Mason Leads No. 1 Kansas Past Oklahoma State, 90-85

lead_paragraph: Kansas had already clinched its 13th consecutive Big 12 regular-season title, so there was nothing on the line against Oklahoma State.
